          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">Navigate the complex visa application process with ease. Our experienced team provides comprehensive visa assistance for all major destinations worldwide.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
